author: smuzaffar
body: This Pr moves `L1Trigger/Phase2L1GMT/interface/Constants.h` header to `DataFormats/L1TMuonPhase2/interface/Constants.h` to avoid dataformats dependency on `L1Trigger/Phase2L1GMT` package. This should fix the FWLite build errors too.
title: Move L1TMuonPhase2/Constants.h to L1TMuonPhase2 dataformat package
